This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and machine translation. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural networks for translation. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it involves the use of attention-based NMT systems. Finally, it could also be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves the evaluation of translation models using various metrics.
